Source: WHO Disease Outbreaks Report, Fri 3 Nov 2000 [edited

Ebola hemorrhagic fever in Uganda - WHO Update 18
--------------------------------------------------
As of Fri 3 Nov 2000, the Ugandan Ministry of Health has reported
cumulative figures of 266 cases of Ebola hemorrhagic fever, with 83 deaths.
[This represents an increase of 4 cases and 2 deaths within the past 24
hours. - Mod.CP
